pigale-1.3.11:
- corrected a bug while taking snapshots of the editor
- added a representation of a bipartite graph on 2 pages
- improved representation of bipartite graphs by contact of segments so that all segments touch or cross the diagonal
- pigale is relinked when libraries change
- added to configure the option --enable-ubuntuto use the preinstalled Qt4 package
- corrected a bug in RemoveIsthmus()
pigale-1.3.10:
- corrected a bug in the server when transfering a graph
- when saving a graph as a text file, an extra line after the title was added
- the random graph generator improved
- when using Qt-4.5.0 the canvas was not properly updated
- by default sample buffers are used if the graphic card is compatible
	

	
